<div class="hint" style="display:block;">
        <h4>{l s='Menu : compound of a menu bar and a set of tabs' mod='innovativemenu'}.</h4>
        <ol style='list-style-type:upper-roman;'>
                <li>{l s='Menu bar: graphics menu with a size, color and font' mod='innovativemenu'}.</li>
                <li>
                        <p>{l s='Tab : menu content that may be a category, a cms, a manufacturer, supplier, or a link. Each tab is linked to a block that contains columns and advertisements.' mod='innovativemenu'}</p>
                        <ol style='list-style-type:lower-alpha; margin-left: 20px'>
                                <li>
                                        <p>{l s='The columns are :' mod='innovativemenu'}</p>
                                        <ul>
                                                <li>
                                                        {l s='Lists lines which depend on the type of tab. Thus, a tab associated with the Class A only contain lists of Category A products or sub categories A or custom links.' mod='innovativemenu'}
                                                </li>
                                                <li>{l s='Text' mod='innovativemenu'}</li>
                                        </ul>
                                <li>{l s='Advertisements can be aligned left, right, top or bottom. They are customizable with text and images.' mod='innovativemenu'}</li>
                        </ol>
                </li>
        </ol>

        <h4>{l s='Create / Edit menu.' mod='innovativemenu'}</h4>
        <ol style='list-style-type:upper-roman;'>
                <li>{l s='Edit the menu name (to find it easily in the menu list created)' mod='innovativemenu'}</li>
                <li>{l s='Edit the menu bar by choosing the size, colors, fonts and then rounding.' mod='innovativemenu'}</li>
                <li>
                        <p>{l s='Edit then the characteristics of each tab.' mod='innovativemenu'}</p>
                        <ol style='list-style-type:lower-alpha; margin-left: 20px'>
                                <li>{l s='If the general configuration menu is activated, all tabs have the general style of the menu bar. Otherwise, edit the colors and fonts of the tab, and columns of the block.' mod='innovativemenu'}</li>
                                <li>{l s='Choose the type of tab then its columns and advertisements.' mod='innovativemenu'}</li>
                        </ol>
                </li>
        </ol>
        
	<p><b>{l s='In a menu, the display order of the tabs can be changed by clicking the up arrow or down arrow. Similarly, in each tab, the order of columns and advertisements can be changed.' mod='innovativemenu'}</b></p>

	<p><b>{l s='Throughout the creation of the menu, a preview is available. It is this insight that will be displayed in the front office. You can create as many menus as desired. One will be displayed, which one is active. Thus, activating a menu disables all others.' mod='innovativemenu'}</b></p>
</div>
